-- Fortis Health, GIC to Defer Preferential Investment in the Indian Company
-- Tuhin Kar
-- 2010-06-25T03:55:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-25/fortis-health-gic-to-defer-preferential-investment-in-the-indian-company.html

          
          
             Fortis Healthcare Ltd. and GIC
Special Investments Pte agreed to defer a planned preferential
investment in the Indian healthcare provider to consider
participating in a larger fund raising by Fortis, according to a
statement today on the Bombay Stock Exchange.   
          
          


  


        